{"tid":2346275,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港的女兒","createTime":"2020-12-30T06:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T09:33:28.000Z","uid":101845,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb30f4c7cc72ebd0a235d4ed3674f58d0a4b172","tid":2346275,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"梅艷芳（英語：Anita Mui Yim-fong，1963年10月10日－2003年<span class=\"red\">12月30日</span>），已故香港歌影壇藝人，有「樂壇大姐大」之稱。她的形象百變，獲獎無數，是香港粵語流行樂壇輝煌極盛期的天皇巨星及標誌性人物，也是香港演藝界第一位取得「歌后」及「影后」級非凡殊榮的女藝人。梅艷芳的影響力不只在演藝界，她更代表了整個香港及華人社會，她去世後被傳媒譽為「香港的女兒」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0zlHGKf44oY&amp;ab_channel=Digitallearning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0zlHGKf44oY%26ab_channel%3DDigitallearning&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSO6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=68c13305\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0zlHGKf44oY&amp;ab_channel=Digitallearning</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WmbHja-Xrbg&amp;ab_channel=wongpanda\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWmbHja-Xrbg%26ab_channel%3Dwongpanda&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSO6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=4ce23335\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WmbHja-Xrbg&amp;ab_channel=wongpanda</a>"},{"pid":"cb4170dca134e929bc9e3520d3a0f8a53d778ba6","tid":2346275,"uid":101845,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:59:09.000Z","msg":"1989年，梅艷芳憑《胭脂扣》獲得第八屆香港電影金像獎最佳女主角獎；同年，八九民運爆發，梅艷芳積極參與，在黃雀行動中出錢出力，結果被中國大陸封殺十年，因而要辭演關錦鵬為她度身訂造的，後來獲得多個獎項的電影《阮玲玉》。<br />\n<br />\n十多年後不少明星開始拒絕評論事件，她自言仍是「民主運動的忠貞分子。」她曾說：「如果我在支持六四方面半途而廢，就會好浪費以前所做的一切，如果我現在放棄，就連一線生機都沒有了。」阿梅說她現在是賭一舖，「<span class=\"red\">我本來已經拿了加拿大passport ，一兩年後會過去居住。六四之前，我會積極去申請居留，但六四之後，我考慮得好清楚，我不要去。我不是那種拿了passport才敢站出來，講說話的人。我搏到九七，在這段期間，我仍會留在香港，盡我最大努力，這麼才說得上無悔今生。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n1989年學運被鎮壓後，她應香港民主派人士之邀，到美國加拿大義演為海外民運團體籌款。香港民主派元老司徒華形容她「有情有義」、「深明大義」。 2004年1月在梅艷芳的葬禮上，前學運領袖吾爾開希獲香港特區政府批准入境，出席梅艷芳的葬禮。"},{"pid":"193f58e22a6bf1b055383de4564721aef5fb1242","tid":2346275,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03447e9e4fb29e787298cc96b9aa3c22488c19a","tid":2346275,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839c2575060d95c45c40769eba01c699b34be74a","tid":2346275,"uid":377416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc69ee724bb1e090424a96cbb14c9eeeacca7cd","tid":2346275,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae900cddd7edab5c0f31f5720ecf510e16c121e5","tid":2346275,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"連登仔太細無人識？"},{"pid":"1eecaf4914fd52049034ec0747d70c1d791f4842","tid":2346275,"uid":38317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"有時會覺得佢走得早係好事<br />\n當年同佢一齊喺台上嘅人依家變到狗都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96091b988e85ce78c3feaa669c7cc762a7abc0e9","tid":2346275,"uid":101845,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1eecaf4914fd52049034ec0747d70c1d791f4842","tid":2346275,"uid":38317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"有時會覺得佢走得早係好